      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really about \"growth\" though. growth implies something new is actually happening. this just feels like... nothing. like there's no point in trying to fix a machine that doesn't even have a soul left in it. i'm just tired of pretending the lights are on when the house is empty.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
